{"tid":764633,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"目標是達成1萬殺！美國盲人玩家在《COD: WWII》遊戲中累計7600殺！","createTime":"2018-08-02T06:17:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-02T17:21:01.000Z","uid":82829,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5720e1b5b9cfa906f0b631fe0b52d7bfce4f263e","tid":764633,"uid":82829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T06:17:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/PSoaKle.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FPSoaKle.jpg&h=86d6e513&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n　　一些FPS玩家在玩FPS遊戲時還未看到敵人身影就一命嗚呼，會戲稱自己是「盲人玩家」，然而在美國，一位真正的盲人玩家憑COD遊戲內的技能設置和一些輔助設備，在《Call of Duty: WWII》這款遊戲中累計達成7600多殺！<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=e7RGLroIz_w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3De7RGLroIz_w&d=5J%2BHlAvnjkhGG%2FU%2Bzg9EiwdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=b2206ce0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=e7RGLroIz_w</a><br />\n<br />\n在Youtube上有一位遊戲Youtber 「tj the blind gamer」，他是一位熱衷於COD遊戲的盲人玩家，在無法看到遊戲畫面的情況下，這位盲人玩家已經在《Call of Duty: WWII》的聯機中累計7600多殺並且目標是達成1萬殺。「tj the blind gamer」是一位視力受損的遊戲玩家，目前生活在美國的猶他州，在他失去視力之前他就是一位COD遊戲玩家，他在8歲的時候熱衷於玩COD世界大戰中的殭屍模式，在現代戰爭2的時候開始玩多人聯機，但那時候他已經只有右眼能看見東西，當他的雙眼完全失去視力後開始玩黑色行動III。<br />\n<br />\n「tj the blind gamer」表示當自己失去視力後再去玩COD遊戲是非常困難的，沒有了視力他只能靠聽覺來判斷敵人的方位，在黑色行動III遊戲中有些技能倒是幫了他，像是Awareness技能可以放大敵人的腳步聲，第六感技能為盲人玩家帶來了特別的聲音效果。最近COD又新增了Alexa技能，容許玩家使用Amazon Alexa 智能音箱提供和接受語音命令，讓「tj the blind gamer」可以獲得更多非視覺資訊！<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/2nFQYvw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F2nFQYvw.jpg&h=22e926df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「tj the blind gamer」對於COD開發小組之一的Treyarch組製作的殭屍系列DLC的高音響效果贊不絕口，他也希望Treyarch組能夠在未來繼續使用相同的遊戲引擎製作COD遊戲中的殭屍模式部分。除了COD外，「tj the blind gamer」也非常喜歡暗黑破壞神3，他希望自己可以成為在COD系列遊戲中最具影響力的盲人玩家。"},{"pid":"ce39dfd386d84cf1b0a2bca6d49d5276cd5b7d48","tid":764633,"uid":11717,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T06:25:51.000Z","msg":"黑色行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dd6f7f179806c35a58a275cee1e3db8aef938c6","tid":764633,"uid":121249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T06:29:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ca1b668f4ca15c3f526dc0ce248b60cbec8247e","tid":764633,"uid":82829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ce39dfd386d84cf1b0a2bca6d49d5276cd5b7d48","tid":764633,"uid":11717,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T06:25:51.000Z","msg":"黑色行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T06:31:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e65a77a98ec69503c3291b6373f5d20df0c9294","tid":764633,"uid":65354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T07:41:46.000Z","msg":"金毛獅王<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw俾佢殺左果啲del game吧啦"},{"pid":"58c5b25836ee04c5b129006f2ea1c1e7238add86","tid":764633,"uid":34517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T08:02:35.000Z","msg":"下次串人可以話盲都玩得叻過你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf96db58ce5adda0eea827087d76efc8aa1740fc","tid":764633,"uid":32906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T17:21:01.000Z","msg":"咁佢kd幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}